{{version032}}
{{flavour|Hurls a large and heavy shard of crystal. It may render a creature's body structure as brittle and fragile as shattered and unrefined crystal, increasing the damage they take from all sources.}}

'''Crystallizing Shot''' is a monster-only spell that launches a shard of crystal. If it hits a target and does any damage, there is a 2/3 chance to apply the [[Fragile]] status for 8-18 turns (up to 50 turns).

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Crystallizing Shot was added in [[0.32]], replacing [[Crystal Bolt]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
